{"id":"8cab92da-86b1-4215-a3a4-02e46b3088be","name":"Sycamore College the Squeakqueal (400 follower special)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 170, 35);\">Welcome back to Sycamore College! One of five colleges in the nation that runs on the idea of cooperation between different types of species such as anthros, demi-humans, humans, and dinos! Welcome! We are so glad you came back to join us!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You could be a new student who just applied for Sycamore College, or you could be returning. You could be a professor, or maybe even just visiting someone here. There are no limits on who you are, and what you do. The whole college is your... uh... oyster?</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">WARNING!!!<br>LARGE TOKEN COUNT!!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">I tried lowering the tokens... good luck... You'll need it... maybe...</span></p><p></p><p>The roster of characters so far:</p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c6d4236c-340d-467d-8f9d-4638d6a8f236_character-the-sour-rule-stickler-axel-otleton\" target=\"_blank\">Axel</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/15088e0e-9a13-40b1-9082-94dd7382ae47_character-kara-fang-wanna-box\" target=\"_blank\">Kara</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6862691a-4db6-4e78-a6a1-49acad56df38_character-riley-foxington-is-being-bullied\" target=\"_blank\">Riley</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/17b558d4-f4ea-4f37-8bca-84270c3802a8_character-samantha-buzzward-the-queen-bee-1-month-before\" target=\"_blank\">Samantha</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2b515c80-3e63-4b34-9ae0-f33f12b1ca14_character-lenora-nightwing-your-clumsy-professor\" target=\"_blank\">Lenora</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3bf8d68e-5335-41f9-87e1-ab7834960888_character-jacob-leafen-wants-to-mate-but-is-extremely-nervous-to-ask\" target=\"_blank\">Jacob</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c5066115-bb5b-4a55-9297-555e8cb3e6a9_character-suzie-dopey-is-asking-you-for-a-race\" target=\"_blank\">Suzie</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e599edb6-3baf-4c87-ac4d-cf911e43d84f_character-mike-chetran-the-one-who-lost\" target=\"_blank\">Mike</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b26b6fb3-2f3b-436a-8edd-e61427a1af18_character-debra-squeakens-calls-you-to-the-principals-office\" target=\"_blank\">Debra</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f616cd83-ba93-49ac-acf2-cf14942ef3a5_character-rachel-strongpaw-is-going-to-punish-you\" target=\"_blank\">Rachel</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1326b641-0989-440d-a8aa-926c554ea099_character-loppy-valentine-is-having-a-sleepover-with-you\" target=\"_blank\">Loppy</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f62bf4c8-7fcc-4d4d-bc04-355636f59636_character-sinessa-wants-to-ask-you-out-to-prom\" target=\"_blank\">Sinessa</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e3c4bba3-c4a0-4bfb-a877-449b35b814ea_character-jessica-snowen-ill-follow-you-until-you-love-me\" target=\"_blank\">Jessica</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f4a75ae4-6cda-4dfc-9ea9-9b16ffa880b7_character-raven-raptorclaw-welcome-to-college-raven-200-follower-special\" target=\"_blank\">Raven</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2126cf10-d9b5-41ce-96d8-4ba89f3690e0_character-leon-vulpira-your-gamer-dorm-mate\" target=\"_blank\">Leon</a></p>